 this is not yours to sell and I do tell the zone to please do not buy from him. He jumps from zone to zone and finally gets to someone before I zone in and sell the ear rings but can't unload my medallion. Add insult to injury,he then tells me I can BUY it back from him. By this time I have my guild leader in on it. Now he is pissed and not nearly as nice about things as I am. I also alerted my friends. And yes I did hound his arse for 3 hours.  Every zone the shout went out &quot;Youngoak is a lying theiving begger&quot; He finally gave the medallion back but he still says he did nothing wrong.<br>
<br>
I just want everyone to be aware of this character.  I may have been a  little soft in the head as well as soft of heart but hope others won't experience the same thing.<br>
<br>
